        Thirty thousand feet.       

39:05.384 --> 39:08.846
          What did you see          
          from 30,000 feet?         

39:08.846 --> 39:11.557
             [rumbling]             

39:11.557 --> 39:13.726
                                   

39:18.773 --> 39:20.691
         [breathes heavily]         

39:21.817 --> 39:24.028
                                   

39:26.989 --> 39:28.532
             [exclaims]             

39:42.838 --> 39:44.548
              [grunts]              

40:05.194 --> 40:06.862
               [pants]              

40:26.966 --> 40:28.926
    [Watt]   Thirty thousand feet.    

40:31.095 --> 40:33.597
        Took you long enough.       

40:35.683 --> 40:36.976
              Careful.              

40:37.476 --> 40:39.937
     The air is thinner up here.    

40:41.772 --> 40:43.566
             [chuckles]             

40:46.777 --> 40:48.112
              [laughs]              

40:51.907 --> 40:53.659
             [laughing]             

